name: Ane The Ballerina
description:
There was a little girl named Ane. She dreamt to be a ballerina. Whoever someone asked what would she become, she'd answer it to be the best ballerina in the world! 

Years passed, but it didn't go well just like what she thought she would be. She was not good enough to be a ballerina because her body was big. Everbody laughed at her. But, it didn't discourage her. She kept doing the ballet, dancing on her own.
